<br>
 <div class="jumbotron">
   <h1>Bloccit</h1>
   <p>Bloccit is a resource for sharing links with your friends!</p>
   <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up pull-right" ></span>
   <% unless current_user %>
   <p>
     <%= link_to "Sign In", new_session_path %> or
     <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> today!
   </p>
   <% end %>
 </div>

 <div class="row">
   <div class="col-md-4">
     <h2>Create topics!</h2>
     <p>Bloccit allows users to create topics for any subject, and allows others to participate in the discussion.</p>
   </div>
   <div class="col-md-4">
     <h2>Vote for your favorite posts!</h2>
     <p>You can upvote/downvote posts and view the most popular topics.</p>
   </div>
   <div class="col-md-4">
     <h2>Make it personal!</h2>
     <p>Customize your profile with an avatar, and show topics/posts you're involved in.</p>
   </div>
 </div>
